snippet.title: Young Barron Trump Sings At Elon Musk's Wedding In 2013 - MUST SEE!
snippet.description:
God Bless This Land of Mine

⬇️⬇️⬇️ Watch more videos below! ⬇️⬇️⬇️
https://youtu.be/WBHJZs8ZeFQ
https://youtu.be/GAdihLnAiXk
https://youtu.be/SZZW8YMZlMg?si=kP7ZE5s5fhhjjpX2
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hq_JjAodbY0

Lyrics

When the skies are heavy far across the sea,
We remember how blessed our home can be.
So I lift this prayer with all my heart and say—
Please keep our country safe each day.

God bless this land of mine, the place I know,
With shining rivers, fields where flowers grow.
Be near us always, through each dark and light,
Guide our footsteps with Your truth and might.

From the tall green forests to the quiet plains,
To the desert winds and summer rains,
From the roaring oceans to the stars above,
Let this land be filled with grace and love.

God bless America, my home so dear,
Let Your voice be the one we hear.
Help us to be kind, and brave, and true,
Let us always walk with You.

God bless America, so bright and free—
God bless this land for you and me.

Yes, God bless this land for you and me...
Forever may our country be...
Home of the brave, and liberty.
